# Project Testing and Validation

Use this file as a pointer to canonical testing and validation requirements.

## Canonical Sources

- `workflow-and-steps.mdc` (validation sequence and reporting)
- `AGENTS.md` (required quality gates and command set)
- `kill-port-3000-before-tests.mdc` (test runner port guard)

## How to Apply

- Run the narrowest checks for touched code first, then broader required checks.
- Respect test preconditions documented in the port guard rule
  before Playwright or Vitest commands.
